DATASET NOTICES
---------------
This repository contains code only. Datasets used in the notebooks are NOT
included in this repository and are subject to their own separate licenses:

- Breast Cancer Wisconsin (Diagnostic): CC BY 4.0
  https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Breast+Cancer+Wisconsin+(Diagnostic)

- Heart Failure Clinical Records: CC BY 4.0
  https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/andrewmvd/heart-failure-clinical-data

- Credit Card Fraud Detection: Open Database License (DbCL v1.0)
  https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud

- MNIST Handwritten Digits: CC BY-SA 3.0
  http://yann.lecun.com/exdb/mnist/

- QM7 Molecular Dataset: CC BY-NC 4.0 (Non-Commercial)
  http://quantum-machine.org/datasets/

Users are responsible for reviewing and complying with the individual licenses
of each dataset before use, redistribution, or incorporation into commercial
products. In particular, the QM7 dataset restricts commercial use.
